[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.9,
    "text": "Honestly, what they say doesn't bother me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.9,
    "endTime": 5.4,
    "text": "I understand we've got an adversarial system."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.4,
    "endTime": 8.08,
    "text": "I'm a mellow sort of guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.08,
    "endTime": 13.379999999999999,
    "text": "And that's why I invited Luther, my anger translator, to join me here tonight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.38,
    "endTime": 33.4,
    "text": "Hold on to your lily-white butts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.4,
    "endTime": 39.278999999999996,
    "text": "In our fast-changing world, traditions like the White House"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.279,
    "endTime": 41.279,
    "text": "Correspondents' Dinner are important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.279,
    "endTime": 43.779,
    "text": "I mean, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.779,
    "endTime": 47.580000000000005,
    "text": "What is this dinner?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.58,
    "endTime": 51.32,
    "text": "And why am I required to come to it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.32,
    "endTime": 55.06,
    "text": "Jeb Bush, do you really want to do this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.06,
    "endTime": 60.660000000000004,
    "text": "Because despite our differences, we count on the press to shed light on the most important issues of the day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.66,
    "endTime": 67.839,
    "text": "And we can count on Fox News to terrify old white people with some nonsense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.839,
    "endTime": 72.44,
    "text": "You realize coming to Cleveland, run for the damn hills!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.44,
    "endTime": 74.699,
    "text": "Y'all is ridiculous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.699,
    "endTime": 76.48,
    "text": "We won't always see eye to eye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.48,
    "endTime": 81.54,
    "text": "Oh, and CNN, thank you so much for the wall-to-wall Ebola coverage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.54,
    "endTime": 86.98,
    "text": "For two whole weeks, we were one step away from the walking dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.98,
    "endTime": 90.76,
    "text": "And then y'all got up and just moved on to the next thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.76,
    "endTime": 91.76,
    "text": "That was awesome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.76,
    "endTime": 94.80000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, and by the way, just if you haven't noticed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.82,
    "endTime": 96.82,
    "text": "I don't have Ebola."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.82,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "But I still deeply appreciate the work that you do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 108.699,
    "text": "Y'all remember when I had that big old hole in the bottom of the Gulf of Mexico, and then I plucked it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.699,
    "endTime": 109.8,
    "text": "Remember that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.8,
    "endTime": 112.94,
    "text": "Which Obama's Katrina was that one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.94,
    "endTime": 113.94,
    "text": "Was that 19?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.94,
    "endTime": 114.94,
    "text": "Or was it 20?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.94,
    "endTime": 115.94,
    "text": "Because I can't remember."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.94,
    "endTime": 121.739,
    "text": "Protecting our democracy is more important than ever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.739,
    "endTime": 124.16000000000001,
    "text": "For example, the Supreme Court ruled that the donor who gave"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.519,
    "endTime": 128.02,
    "text": "Ted Cruz $6 million was just exercising free speech."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.02,
    "endTime": 130.52,
    "text": "Yeah, it's the kind of speech like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.52,
    "endTime": 132.52,
    "text": "I just wasted $6 million."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.52,
    "endTime": 137.399,
    "text": "And it's not just Republicans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.399,
    "endTime": 139.94,
    "text": "Hillary will have to raise huge sums of money, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.94,
    "endTime": 140.94,
    "text": "Oh, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.94,
    "endTime": 143.94,
    "text": "She gonna get that money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.94,
    "endTime": 148.94,
    "text": "She gonna get all the money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.94,
    "endTime": 153.94,
    "text": "Khaleesi is coming to Westeros."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.699,
    "endTime": 159.699,
    "text": "Watch out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.699,
    "endTime": 168.179,
    "text": "The non-stop focus on billionaire donors creates real problems for our democracy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.179,
    "endTime": 170.179,
    "text": "And that's why we're running for a third term!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.179,
    "endTime": 171.179,
    "text": "No, we're not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.179,
    "endTime": 172.179,
    "text": "We're not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.179,
    "endTime": 177.179,
    "text": "Who the hell said that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.179,
    "endTime": 180.86,
    "text": "But we do need to stay focused on some big challenges, like climate change."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.86,
    "endTime": 181.86,
    "text": "Hey, listen, y'all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.88,
    "endTime": 186.779,
    "text": "If you haven't noticed, California is bone dry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.779,
    "endTime": 191.619,
    "text": "It look like a trailer for the new Mad Max movie up in there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.619,
    "endTime": 197.66,
    "text": "Y'all think that Bradley Cooper came here because he wants to talk to Chuck Todd?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.66,
    "endTime": 199.66,
    "text": "He needed a glass of water!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.66,
    "endTime": 202.94,
    "text": "Come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.94,
    "endTime": 204.94,
    "text": "The science is clear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.479,
    "endTime": 207.479,
    "text": "The science is clear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.5,
    "endTime": 213.25900000000001,
    "text": "Nine out of the ten hottest years ever came in the last decade."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.259,
    "endTime": 216.23999999999998,
    "text": "Now, I'm not a scientist, but I do know how to count to ten."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.24,
    "endTime": 218.839,
    "text": "Rising seas, more violent storms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.839,
    "endTime": 224.139,
    "text": "You got mosquitoes, sweaty people on the train stinking it up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.139,
    "endTime": 225.779,
    "text": "It's just nasty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.779,
    "endTime": 230.619,
    "text": "I mean, look at what's happening right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.619,
    "endTime": 233.479,
    "text": "Every serious scientist says we need to act."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.479,
    "endTime": 237.22000000000003,
    "text": "The Pentagon says it's a national security risk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.96,
    "endTime": 244.059,
    "text": "Miami floods on a sunny day, and instead of doing anything about it, we've got elected officials throwing snowballs in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.059,
    "endTime": 245.059,
    "text": "Senate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.059,
    "endTime": 246.8,
    "text": "Okay, I think I got it, bro."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.8,
    "endTime": 248.639,
    "text": "It is crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.639,
    "endTime": 250.139,
    "text": "What about our kids?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.139,
    "endTime": 254.639,
    "text": "What kind of stupid, short-sighted, irresponsible bull.."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.639,
    "endTime": 255.639,
    "text": "Whoa, whoa, whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.639,
    "endTime": 256.64,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.64,
    "endTime": 257.64,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.64,
    "endTime": 258.64,
    "text": "Okay, no, hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.64,
    "endTime": 259.64,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.64,
    "endTime": 261.64,
    "text": "All due respect, sir, you don't need an anger translator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.64,
    "endTime": 262.64,
    "text": "You need counseling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.64,
    "endTime": 263.64,
    "text": "I'm out of here, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.64,
    "endTime": 265.64,
    "text": "I ain't trying to get into all this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.64,
